* Fix {{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8216}}: Don't show floating text on autoreplace if cost is 0 ({{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8244}})
* Fix {{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8129}}: Crash if a news message expires while viewing the endgame screen ({{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8243}})
* Fix {{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8221}}: Use more specific error message when a bridge is too long ({{en/Development/Design Drafts/GHIssue|8240}})
